Preheat the oven to 180C/350F/Gas 4.To make the caramelised pineapple, melt the butter for 2-3 minutes in an oven-proof saucepan.  Add pineapple wedges, brown sugar and vanilla.Place into the preheated oven for four minutes.To make the sabayon, over a pan of simmering water place the sabayon ingredients into a bowl.  Whisk constantly over medium heat until light and doubled in size, for 3-4 minutes.Serve the caramelised pineapple with the sabayon sauce on the side.